Orim Music – We are the modern alternative to the traditional burdensome of obtaining public performance license in compositions and masters. Being the first non-governmental affiliated entity in Nigeria to offer onestop performing rights licensing hub means that we have to be innovative and efficient, but more importantly make licensing simple. Our business model is to offer music users the opportunity to play their favour songs and pay royalties for just the songs they played. We are recruiting to fill the position below: Location: Lagos Application Closing Date
